## ğŸ“„ Privacy Policy

### 1. Data Collection
The **Counter App** does not collect, store, or share any personal or usage data. All counter values and to-do list tasks are stored locally on your device.

### 2. Third-Party Services
This app does not integrate with or use any third-party services for analytics, advertising, or data collection.

### 3. Permissions
The app requires no special permissions to operate and respects your privacy.

### 4. Updates to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page. We encourage you to review this page periodically for any updates.

### 5. Contact Us
